layers.nm: An incredible season that started brilliantly, with the Reds as the best team in the world and clear favorites to win every possible trophy. Although the pace dipped a bit, winning the Premier League with the fans at home is amazing. Slot showed what he's capable of, and the team feels very strong heading into next season.  YNWA forever...
